track_notes: This route starts in Glen Douglas, goes up to Beinn Bhreac SS-081. It then descends and rises to the col at An t-Srean. We then go up to SS-103 Tulloch Hill. After the activation there we retreat the same way but go left at the col to return to our hotel at Loch Long in Arrochar. Although I say it myself this was an excellent route!
